{"tid":130031,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"始終都係wow好,咩黑沙根本唔入流","createTime":"2017-02-22T05:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T09:46:25.000Z","uid":3374,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5efbbc46cc4fcc4caf570a149cc5dd4e84407d5","tid":130031,"uid":3374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:35:28.000Z","msg":"差唔多玩左十年 年年都有人話過氣 沒落 就執 但依加仲大大隻企係度 <br />\n好記得以前成日有新game比人話取代wow e.g 劍靈 <br />\n結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加又有隻黑色沙漠吹到好衡 我個wow公會仲拉大隊去玩 但一個月未夠已經死哂返艾澤拉斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底幾時先可以轉game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  泡菜啲game廠爭氣啲啦  玩黎玩去都係買張點卡之後老尾farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0764887ff5cd72cbcce2ef0360cfe96006ab90b","tid":130031,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"未玩過wow, 但係黑色真係單機game黎"},{"pid":"3e346e94bdc3dad58aecfc7944434329afb369d0","tid":130031,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"吹大咗<br />\n鬼佬SER一堆死城"},{"pid":"83c33909090142f75ba2a567efbf3d8f96af10fb","tid":130031,"uid":3374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未玩過wow, 但係黑色真係單機game黎</blockquote><br />\n玩法單機 但交易方法好似搶平安米咁我屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個地圖系統就直頭戇鳩 騎住隻蓄牲跑幾個字以為自己好撚有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467727a2e0930e52c823d744500ded603d43adb9","tid":130031,"uid":172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:48:41.000Z","msg":"黑色沙漠初初玩覺得幾好玩 但玩左個幾禮拜覺得日日好似一直做緊同一樣野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個生活系統係就好似好 多野玩 但其實又係騎住馬仔周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n本身頭幾日玩見佢個戰場好似幾正 打大交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到升到50幾lv 啲裝整到7788 入去玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你中大伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本唔會知發生緊咩事 出到去亂扔技唔知咩事殺左個 人轉個頭自己條血又係唔知咩事無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  兩日無on了 成隻game不停重覆緊騎馬去一個地方再騎返去另一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5922b775c940e7bd815dde817da362cf382d0ce4","tid":130031,"uid":12083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"跟本唔好玩 c9 馬英果d 仲好玩過佢"},{"pid":"e93edfdb75635d4bc95355abd9a0e19d76aab012","tid":130031,"uid":3374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑色沙漠初初玩覺得幾好玩 但玩左個幾禮拜覺得日日好似一直做緊同一樣野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個生活系統係就好似好 多野玩 但其實又係騎住馬仔周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n本身頭幾日玩見佢個戰場好似幾正 打大交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到升到50幾lv 啲裝整到7788 入去玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你中大伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本唔會知發生緊咩事 出到去亂扔技唔知咩事殺左個 人轉個頭自己條血又係唔知咩事無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  兩日無on了 成隻game不停重覆緊騎馬去一個地方再騎返去另一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以其實唔無魔獸勁 <br />\n係次次啲所謂大作、神作垃圾 比人吹得太大<br />\n明明我wow玩到悶悶地 玩完啲新game死返去又會突然覺得wow好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38af0398567c4a818ccb516e151d2b3153043f37","tid":130031,"uid":3374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黑色沙漠初初玩覺得幾好玩 但玩左個幾禮拜覺得日日好似一直做緊同一樣野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個生活系統係就好似好 多野玩 但其實又係騎住馬仔周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n本身頭幾日玩見佢個戰場好似幾正 打大交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到升到50幾lv 啲裝整到7788 入去玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你中大伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本唔會知發生緊咩事 出到去亂扔技唔知咩事殺左個 人轉個頭自己條血又係唔知咩事無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  兩日無on了 成隻game不停重覆緊騎馬去一個地方再騎返去另一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以其實唔係魔獸勁 <br />\n係次次啲所謂大作、神作垃圾 比人吹得太大<br />\n明明我wow玩到悶悶地 玩完啲新game死返去又會突然覺得wow好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"34c9ddb92f5c9b7c9e87e00b89d9d6daca12e66c","tid":130031,"uid":17286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔好玩 c9 馬英果d 仲好玩過佢</blockquote><br />\nTrue<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲dum左百幾蚊落去<br />\n坦白講句<br />\n垃圾game+賤格營運商<br />\n吹谷到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d617add3d6296657ce4bb097bf9ec632cea4baf4","tid":130031,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"wow垃圾拖月費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34016ea3e45b5b8a977918037a92ea1791e9b8e4","tid":130031,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"老老實實玩生活未輪到黑沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩打擊感瑪英贏佢幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑沙真係玩畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，瑪英撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎一齊玩"},{"pid":"981ace61e695440dab79f84116e6b87da23459ac","tid":130031,"uid":3374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老實實玩生活未輪到黑沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩打擊感瑪英贏佢幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑沙真係玩畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，瑪英撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n啲泡菜game真係得個畫面見得人 劇情又廢 世界觀又廢 最撚叻就收你錢再由你老尾咁farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講打怪個爽度又唔夠無雙爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個生活仲撚on9 日頭返完工夜晚開機返第二份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好笑係外國ser個個唔撚玩啦 依加出個中文ser成班係度跟風玩 十足十之前pkm go咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話我打手都無所謂 MMORPG 得3隻： Runescape, wow, 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d020ed9688e56c353063685530eca0e09e48a5d","tid":130031,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老老實實玩生活未輪到黑沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩打擊感瑪英贏佢幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑沙真係玩畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，瑪英撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n啲泡菜game真係得個畫面見得人 劇情又廢 世界觀又廢 最撚叻就收你錢再由你老尾咁farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講打怪個爽度又唔夠無雙爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個生活仲撚on9 日頭返完工夜晚開機返第二份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好笑係外國ser個個唔撚玩啦 依加出個中文ser成班係度跟風玩 十足十之前pkm go咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話我打手都無所謂 MMORPG 得3隻： Runescape, wow, 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwow係高汁，中學嗰陣真係放學打到十二點比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死騎一出嗰排可以話唔洗訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BTW啲同學中三開始就冇玩，我單機到中五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ba65724a6bfbcda29cac7a730a9e14000858a9","tid":130031,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老老實實玩生活未輪到黑沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩打擊感瑪英贏佢幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑沙真係玩畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，瑪英撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n啲泡菜game真係得個畫面見得人 劇情又廢 世界觀又廢 最撚叻就收你錢再由你老尾咁farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講打怪個爽度又唔夠無雙爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個生活仲撚on9 日頭返完工夜晚開機返第二份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好笑係外國ser個個唔撚玩啦 依加出個中文ser成班係度跟風玩 十足十之前pkm go咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話我打手都無所謂 MMORPG 得3隻： Runescape, wow, 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwow係高汁，中學嗰陣真係放學打到十二點比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死騎一出嗰排可以話唔洗訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BTW啲同學中三開始就冇玩，我單機到中五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係瑪英真心好玩，摸技術已經要大量時間；<br />\n之後慢慢搞裝，再練技術，玩到可以SOLO各Boss之後嘅滿足感真係正到冇人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重點就係，到依家仲不停更新緊好多野，新武器，改善系統等等&hellip;&hellip;真係有心嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外可以唔洗課都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過係慢啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3d354153e6179d4dc33d0ca73ee4818748ff11","tid":130031,"uid":3374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老老實實玩生活未輪到黑沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩打擊感瑪英贏佢幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑沙真係玩畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，瑪英撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n啲泡菜game真係得個畫面見得人 劇情又廢 世界觀又廢 最撚叻就收你錢再由你老尾咁farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講打怪個爽度又唔夠無雙爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個生活仲撚on9 日頭返完工夜晚開機返第二份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好笑係外國ser個個唔撚玩啦 依加出個中文ser成班係度跟風玩 十足十之前pkm go咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話我打手都無所謂 MMORPG 得3隻： Runescape, wow, 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwow係高汁，中學嗰陣真係放學打到十二點比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死騎一出嗰排可以話唔洗訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BTW啲同學中三開始就冇玩，我單機到中五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係瑪英真心好玩，摸技術已經要大量時間；<br />\n之後慢慢搞裝，再練技術，玩到可以SOLO各Boss之後嘅滿足感真係正到冇人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重點就係，到依家仲不停更新緊好多野，新武器，改善系統等等&hellip;&hellip;真係有心嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外可以唔洗課都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過係慢啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n瑪英互動性都完爆黑沙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  黑沙比自閉仔玩都厭悶 會一齊打既野每日得幾隻 之後就去騎馬睇風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時間會證明一切 隻隻挑戰wow既game下場都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n為賺錢既game係唔會贏到真正既game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cad437796c648078318df328012ef12c93aa75","tid":130031,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"wow 去到版本中期咪又係悶到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3e4bb9b0276bf3f88b843c9c5f22e87b8f9016","tid":130031,"uid":5971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>wow 去到版本中期咪又係悶到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無可否認wow真係無可取代"},{"pid":"32ee6177c12961e0d32bb2b93a7f2e65b6aba4d0","tid":130031,"uid":20219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite